<div class="separator" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #2e2e2e; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;" align="center"><a style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; text-decoration-line: none; color: #000000;" href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YSuUF4hfxKQ/VrFKEwIdIeI/AAAAAAAAAFo/SD02fE0PsTA/s1600/20160130075159.jpg"><span style="font-family: times, td_ptktimes new romantd_ptk, serif;"><img style="margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; border-width: initial; border-style: none; position: relative; max-width: 100%;" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YSuUF4hfxKQ/VrFKEwIdIeI/AAAAAAAAAFo/SD02fE0PsTA/s400/20160130075159.jpg" width="400" height="297" border="0" /></span></a></div>
